snippet.title: Candy Conveyor
snippet.description: Candy Conveyor Puzzle game. Add conveyor belts to the chains in order to get the right candy at the right place.

snippet.title: Canyon Glider
snippet.description: Canyon Glider Fly your glider through the canyons. Try to avoid the birds and catch the rings for extra points.

snippet.title: Canyon Defence
snippet.description: Canyon Defence Defend your canyons and buy several upgrades to get better towers and kill the enemy troops.

snippet.title: Canyon Shooter
snippet.description: Canyon Shooter Metal Slug style game. Fight your way through the canyons taking out the enemy on the way down.

snippet.title: Fashion Designer New York
snippet.description: Fashion Designer New York Create a casual, a professional and a dressy outfit for the fashion show in NY.

snippet.title: Youda Camper
snippet.description: Youda Camper Become a campsite owner in this adventurous management game similar to Simcity.

snippet.title: Youda Conqueror
snippet.description: Youda Conqueror Match at least three bubbles of the same kind to gather resources to build your palaces.

snippet.title: Samurai Master: Road to Tokyo
snippet.description: Samurai Master: Road to Tokyo Use your impeccable samurai skills to defeat the many enemies.

snippet.title: Youda Farmer
snippet.description: Youda Farmer Run your own farm. Grow crops, keep chickens, etc. and provide the shops the supplies they need.

snippet.title: Youda Marina
snippet.description: Youda Marina Harbor simulation game. Create and mangage an efficient working harbor and make a lot of money.
